{"tid":1313600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[衝突開端]護住條肥佬嗰班狗 真係畜牲都不如","createTime":"2019-07-13T22:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T22:34:09.000Z","uid":44423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"489ebf1edf1a092806c532352498b6e6e1c1a084","tid":1313600,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:16:11.000Z","msg":"首先 714需要大家 希望得閒嘅都可以出下去<br />\n<br />\n大約4：30pm <br />\n<br />\n一開始大家都係和理非咁遊行<br />\n去到屈人寺嗰個位<br />\n聽聞條肥佬用電話影鳩手足<br />\n(聽聞)有人用手拍低佢部電話<br />\n個肥佬郁手 成班人咪圍佢<br />\n點知班狗仔護住個肥佬上天橋<br />\n有幾個兄弟都知班狗想放人<br />\n咪一齊上天橋圍鳩個肥佬<br />\n一開始橋上面都唔算太多手足<br />\n點知條天橋有人係上面丟左個水樽同一個罐落黎<br />\n有啲企係樓下嘅手足咪忍唔住一齊上天橋捉人<br />\n上到去就見到兄弟們都圍鳩住個肥佬<br />\n有幾隻狗仔企係肥佬隔離護住佢<br />\n大家都一齊叫狗仔拉人 佢地又護住個肥佬唔做野<br />\n大家圍屌左佢地幾分鐘 就有一批狗上去增援<br />\n啲狗入去嗰時係咁推撞啲兄弟<br />\n啲兄弟比佢地撞開左 啲狗反而話人地郁佢襲警(黑人問號？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n佢地成班人護住個肥佬 想帶個肥佬出去<br />\n推撞期間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HdJ2TA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdJ2TA9.jpg&h=a0d239bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzDm89A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzDm89A.jpg&h=88a1aa15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻護主犬就叉住其中一位兄弟條頸長達十秒<br />\n<br />\n過左一陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFcCHs1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFcCHs1.jpg&h=0b7e85ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位絲打就話隻狗(同上面同一隻)摸到佢<br />\n比狗非禮要求報警 要狗仔編號 同埋報案編號<br />\n隻狗仔show左張證就急急腳走左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPGskhx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPGskhx.jpg&h=da546a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSW74Kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSW74Kd.jpg&h=ca33644a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻狗就專扯人口罩比隔離隻狗用cam影樣<br />\n<br />\n去到後尾大家都應該知道有記者同兄弟比班狗推到跌左落地下(有片) 呢度唔多講了<br />\n<br />\n為左護住個肥佬走 仲出埋椒 (都有其他片睇到)<br />\n<br />\n班狗護住個肥佬去條橋往彩園方向<br />\n橋上嘅兄弟就開始叫仲遊行緊嘅兄弟去嗰邊橋嘅樓梯進行反包抄 <br />\n啲狗又開始call增援<br />\n就發生後面嘅事<br />\n<br />\n其實班狗一開始拉左條肥佬 根本就唔會發生後面所有嘅事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死黑警 屌你老母</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5b5db48e7cfae57215694570b49f57d68c130138","tid":1313600,"uid":44423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:32:11.000Z","msg":"求求大家去沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a50b1d7e0b2b52fce8ce187c3c53fff02397173","tid":1313600,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:32:21.000Z","msg":"求求大家去沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7f75fcf54dc36d9df953b95cd3c683cd98a795","tid":1313600,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:32:31.000Z","msg":"求求大家去沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1333c03f59bbf7309a0420454b22bbb7a0299b86","tid":1313600,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:32:41.000Z","msg":"求求大家去沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d07bf9c6821a278336ef96e4c6c237b295fad29","tid":1313600,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:32:51.000Z","msg":"求求大家去沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im